1
00:00:11,090 --> 00:00:14,080
”Three Lives, Three Worlds” by Jason Zhang

2
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:17,570
♫ Listen to the rustling of the wind ♫

3
00:00:17,570 --> 00:00:20,970
♫ Whose sorrow is it trying to stir up? ♫

4
00:00:20,970 --> 00:00:24,620
♫ My yearning grows so instantaneously ♫

5
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:28,260
♫ That I forget how long the night is ♫

6
00:00:28,260 --> 00:00:31,420
♫ I hold the tears in my palm until they become burning hot ♫

7
00:00:31,420 --> 00:00:35,270
♫ I’m only willing to be crazy for you for three lifetimes ♫

8
00:00:35,270 --> 00:00:38,840
♫ Falling blossoms are everywhere, and I also smell the fragrance of the zither ♫

9
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:42,350
♫ With you, I wander the world ♫

10
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,900
♫  If love is too desolate, I will dream this dream with you ♫

11
00:00:45,900 --> 00:00:49,450
♫ And redeem all your tears ♫

12
00:00:49,450 --> 00:00:52,970
♫ No matter how far this journey will be or how long these three lifetimes will be ♫

13
00:00:52,970 --> 00:00:56,430
♫ We will be hand in hand until eternity ♫

14
00:00:56,430 --> 00:01:00,020
♫ Despite the miserable wind, vast fog, rolling storm, or overflowing snow ♫

15
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:03,660
♫ I will walk with you every step of the way ♫

16
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:07,120
♫ I will hold your hand, don’t be alarmed, don’t worry about tomorrow ♫

17
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:10,670
♫ Even if we are destined to wander the world ♫

18
00:01:10,670 --> 00:01:14,170
♫ Even if we travel to the remotest corners of Earth ♫

19
00:01:14,170 --> 00:01:16,000
♫ Never let go of each other’s hands ♫

20
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,780
♫ Never forget our mutual love ♫

21
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:21,230
♫ Life does not need to be too brilliant ♫

22
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:24,770
♫ Empty glories eventually become nothing, those things you persisted will leave with the wind ♫

23
00:01:24,770 --> 00:01:28,120
♫ Why is love full of ups and downs? ♫

24
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:31,810
♫ How many storms do we have to face before our hearts stop wavering? ♫

25
00:01:31,810 --> 00:01:34,560
♫ Let’s run through our past together ♫

26
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:38,880
♫ I’ll wait with you for the wind to stop, fog to clear, rain to end, and snow to melt ♫

27
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:42,150
♫ Before seeing the absolute beautiful moon again ♫

28
00:01:42,150 --> 00:01:46,560
♫ I will still be by your side ♫

29
00:02:00,750 --> 00:02:05,020
[Eternal Love]

30
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:12,910
[Episode 39]

31
00:02:15,420 --> 00:02:17,080
And you?

32
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:22,840
When my affection for you was the strongest, you gave me a big blow.

33
00:02:23,570 --> 00:02:25,980
You only know that I let go quickly and confidently,

34
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:30,880
but you don't know that behind it, I went through so much heartache.

35
00:02:31,950 --> 00:02:35,730
That year, when Teacher died,

36
00:02:35,730 --> 00:02:38,910
I forcefully brought a humble heart

37
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:42,390
and went to your Grand Purple Palace to borrow the Jaded Soul.

38
00:02:42,390 --> 00:02:47,260
You will never understand how much courage I mustered.

39
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:53,830
And you won't ever understand how much you had disappointed me.

40
00:02:55,070 --> 00:02:57,360
It wasn't like that.

41
00:02:57,360 --> 00:03:00,370
I didn't know how seriously injured you were then.

42
00:03:00,370 --> 00:03:04,860
If you have told me that you used the blood from your heart to preserve Mo Yuan's body,

43
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:07,260
I would have given it to you.

44
00:03:08,690 --> 00:03:13,380
I didn't give you the Jaded Soul because I knew you were protecting Mo Yuan.

45
00:03:14,010 --> 00:03:17,030
Yes, I was jealous.

46
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:19,050
I was jealous of Mo Yuan.

47
00:03:19,050 --> 00:03:21,090
But Ah Yin,

48
00:03:21,090 --> 00:03:26,010
the truth is... is that I've never forgotten you.

49
00:03:27,730 --> 00:03:29,760
Can you forgive me?

50
00:03:39,260 --> 00:03:42,630
Winged Monarch, you are telling me now that you have never forgotten me?

51
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:50,340
It's because you are constantly pursuing something you can't have or something you have lost.

52
00:03:53,180 --> 00:03:56,990
But once you get it, you won't treasure it anymore.

53
00:03:59,970 --> 00:04:04,750
Are you just saying this to lessen your own burden?

54
00:04:07,950 --> 00:04:11,270
You never actually loved me, right?

55
00:04:13,530 --> 00:04:16,080
After the incident with Xuan Nü and me,

56
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:18,980
you let go so quickly

57
00:04:18,980 --> 00:04:22,160
because you were already disgusted with me. Right?

58
00:04:28,370 --> 00:04:31,160
But everyone makes mistakes.

59
00:04:31,820 --> 00:04:34,170
You're my only love.

60
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:38,200
Why can't you forgive me?

61
00:04:41,310 --> 00:04:44,200
You did such a thing back then.

62
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:47,880
Do you wish for Xuan Nü and me to share the same husband?

63
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:57,450
When I left Grand Purple Palace, I was definitely angry and hated you.

64
00:04:57,450 --> 00:05:02,020
But after losing so much blood in Splendid Flame Cave and I was hanging on for life,

65
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:06,670
I discovered that the face in my head wasn't you at all.

66
00:05:07,450 --> 00:05:09,750
I knew then...

67
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:12,890
that I was not heartbroken,

68
00:05:12,890 --> 00:05:14,620
that I was finally free.

69
00:05:14,620 --> 00:05:16,830
Ah Yin! Don't say that.

70
00:05:21,810 --> 00:05:25,980
Li Jing, you are indeed

71
00:05:25,980 --> 00:05:30,130
the only man that I loved in these 140,000 years,

72
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:36,290
but time changes everything.

73
00:05:36,290 --> 00:05:38,120
We can't go back to how we used to be.

74
00:05:39,710 --> 00:05:42,140
I understood too late.

75
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:44,890
And you...

76
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:49,580
won't remain in the same spot to wait for me.

77
00:05:53,230 --> 00:05:56,860
Let's be strangers from now on.

78
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,190
Goodbye.

79
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:37,550
They were such sweet words,

80
00:06:37,550 --> 00:06:42,030
but the way you say it sounds so hurtful.

81
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:48,060
Look at the sky.

82
00:06:48,060 --> 00:06:50,350
It might rain soon.

83
00:06:51,050 --> 00:06:52,960
Let's go.

84
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:20,790
- High God, are you looking for Great Lady?
- Yes.

85
00:07:20,790 --> 00:07:23,080
Didn't she just come back last night?

86
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:25,490
- Where did she go again?
- She went to Heavenly Palace.

87
00:07:25,490 --> 00:07:29,090
His Highness the Crown Prince said that Lord of Lingbao has a Heavenly Spring Pool in High Clear Plane.

88
00:07:29,090 --> 00:07:32,860
Soaking in it will help to heal Great Lady's injury, so he brought her to Nine Heavens.

89
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:34,770
Where's Zhen Zhen then?

90
00:07:34,770 --> 00:07:36,590
Fourth Uncle went to the market.

91
00:07:36,590 --> 00:07:40,890
He said that he wanted to personally choose some ingredients to cook for you.

92
00:07:40,890 --> 00:07:43,790
He's not Fengjiu. His cooking is terrible.

93
00:07:43,790 --> 00:07:45,960
He's torturing me.

94
00:07:47,090 --> 00:07:50,200
By the way, I'm here for another important matter.

95
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:54,720
A few days ago, when Young Fifth brought Mo Yuan back, did she leave him in Splendid Flame Cave?

96
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:57,300
Yes, High God Mo Yuan is still there.

97
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:59,290
But Great Lady didn't leave him there.

98
00:07:59,290 --> 00:08:02,020
When she came back, she was seriously injured and unconscious.

99
00:08:02,020 --> 00:08:05,800
His Highness the Crown Prince personally brought High God Mo Yuan back.

100
00:08:07,070 --> 00:08:09,750
While Zhen Zhen is not back yet, take me to see Mo Yuan.

101
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:12,440
Okay. High God, please come with me.

102
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,640
I will go in alone. You can go back first.

103
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:30,320
Yes.

104
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:33,650
For the time being, don't let anyone know that I came to visit Mo Yuan.

105
00:08:35,150 --> 00:08:37,090
Yes, High God.

106
00:09:05,850 --> 00:09:09,820
Zhe Yan! Come drink with me.

107
00:09:10,690 --> 00:09:11,990
What wine?

108
00:09:11,990 --> 00:09:14,310
It definitely can't be better than mine.

109
00:09:14,310 --> 00:09:17,100
Looks like you wasted money again.

110
00:09:17,100 --> 00:09:18,820
This is the best wine in Green Hill.

111
00:09:18,820 --> 00:09:21,090
Just make do.

112
00:09:22,450 --> 00:09:27,170
Even if I want to, I fear that I can't do it today.

113
00:09:27,170 --> 00:09:29,300
I need to rush back to Ten Miles of Peach Blossoms forest.

114
00:09:29,300 --> 00:09:31,100
Going back there?

115
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:34,660
Didn't you say that you were going to stay in the fox den for a few days?

116
00:09:35,610 --> 00:09:39,340
I thought of a way that could save the eldest prince of the Western Sea,

117
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:43,680
but I need to rush back to the Peach Forest to flip through my medical books.

118
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:45,620
Really?

119
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:47,850
Go back now.

120
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,670
Go now and come back soon.

121
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,410
It's indeed as I expected.

122
00:10:04,410 --> 00:10:08,500
This Kunlun Void is a divine mountain that grew from a dragon bone.

123
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:11,140
When Mo Yuan left, it became deserted.

124
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:17,010
But now, there's a faint dragon energy moving below it.

125
00:10:17,010 --> 00:10:20,060
This place is indeed abnormal.

126
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:30,040
High God Zhe Yan.

127
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:32,030
You are...?

128
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:35,040
Second Disciple of Kunlun Void.

129
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:42,380
I met you before when Si Yin first met her teacher.

130
00:10:42,380 --> 00:10:46,180
Yes, it was during that time that I had the honor to meet you.

131
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:48,210
Just now, when I was feeding Teacher's divine cranes,

132
00:10:48,210 --> 00:10:51,800
I heard them calling and I knew that an important guest was here.

133
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:54,780
I didn't expect that it would be you, High God.

134
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:57,770
High God, I wonder why you are here.

135
00:10:57,770 --> 00:11:01,260
What can I do for you?

136
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:02,890
When Father God passed away,

137
00:11:02,890 --> 00:11:07,560
I once eternally sealed the divine weapon Zither of Fuxi under the Kunlun Mountain.

138
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:10,280
In the blink of an eye, many years have passed.

139
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:13,920
I suddenly miss this old partner, so I came to take a look.

140
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,430
I see.

141
00:11:15,430 --> 00:11:17,870
I had heard Teacher mention this magical weapon before.

142
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:20,660
High God, this way, please.

143
00:11:27,910 --> 00:11:31,580
You are the only disciple left in Kunlun Void?

144
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:37,750
These past 70,000 years, some disciples return home if they have family affairs,

145
00:11:37,750 --> 00:11:41,620
and those that don't, go and look for Teacher and Seventeenth's whereabouts.

146
00:11:41,620 --> 00:11:45,100
A few days ago, Zi Lan came back and cleaned up this place.

147
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:49,170
Then, Winged Monarch came, saying he saw Si Yin.

148
00:11:49,170 --> 00:11:52,250
Zi Lan was so excited and said he would go to the Mortal Realm to find him

149
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:55,310
and asked me to take care of the cranes.

150
00:11:55,310 --> 00:11:58,900
Oh? The Winged Monarch said he saw Si Yin?

151
00:12:00,950 --> 00:12:03,040
I don't know if he was telling the truth,

152
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:06,750
but Zi Lan couldn't sit still and went to find him.

153
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:31,010
Even Green Hill's entrance has Mi Gu watching at least.

154
00:12:31,010 --> 00:12:34,090
This Eternal Heavenly Realm of yours made of 36 heavens...

155
00:12:34,090 --> 00:12:35,910
There's not even a single guard here.

156
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:37,900
Doesn't look imposing at all.

157
00:12:39,770 --> 00:12:42,320
Today, Old Monarch Taishang is having a public Dao lecture.

158
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,760
I reckon they went to the assembly.

159
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:48,740
So, there's a religious assembly.

160
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:53,760
Qian Qian, I heard that when you were in the mortal realm to help Yuan Zhen with his tribulation,

161
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:56,100
you often discussed Daoism with Yuan Zhen.

162
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:58,790
I'm sure you now have a deep knowledge of Dao.

163
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:08,950
For tens of thousands of years, Old Monarch Taishang can be considered as unrivaled in speeches.

164
00:13:08,950 --> 00:13:11,140
He's at the very top,

165
00:13:11,140 --> 00:13:13,350
and you can say that he's been very lonely.

166
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:18,410
Now that you are here, you can debate with him.

167
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:23,770
Well said. Well said.

168
00:13:26,590 --> 00:13:35,210
[Pure Wutong Palace]

169
00:13:35,210 --> 00:13:37,980
I hear when you were 30,000 years old, you set up the office for military affairs,

170
00:13:37,980 --> 00:13:40,460
and Heavenly Monarch named this Pure Wutong Palace.

171
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:43,000
That's right.

172
00:13:45,540 --> 00:13:48,630
But this place is so dim.

173
00:13:48,630 --> 00:13:52,290
It looks like the Crystal Palace of the Eastern Sea during that 100-day old celebration.

174
00:13:53,270 --> 00:13:55,700
It's because you can't look at glaring light.

175
00:13:58,700 --> 00:14:00,910
Because of me?

176
00:14:04,330 --> 00:14:06,130
Qian Qian.

177
00:14:10,690 --> 00:14:12,860
I'll take you inside.

178
00:14:28,970 --> 00:14:32,970
I didn't imagine that we would need to jump in when we would come to Nine Heavens

179
00:14:32,970 --> 00:14:35,250
and not be able to even take the main gate.

180
00:14:37,050 --> 00:14:42,210
If we walked through the main gate, we would surely alarm all the courtyards here.

181
00:14:42,210 --> 00:14:44,890
It would be annoyingly noisy.

182
00:14:45,390 --> 00:14:47,820
It's more convenient to jump over the wall.

183
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:52,030
That's reasonable.

184
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:58,010
By the way, we came early today.

185
00:14:58,010 --> 00:15:02,110
It's still not the time for that Little Immortal Jia Yun to deliver you your official documents.

186
00:15:02,110 --> 00:15:06,200
Did you not tell him to stop sending documents to Green Hill

187
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:08,590
and are causing him to go there in vain?

188
00:15:14,250 --> 00:15:16,870
What you just said makes sense.

189
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:20,750
Fortunately, we didn't use the main door and alert the little immortals.

190
00:15:21,710 --> 00:15:23,910
If not, it would be troublesome.

191
00:15:27,110 --> 00:15:31,380
But talking about this, we went home late yesterday,

192
00:15:31,380 --> 00:15:33,880
so many documents have accumulated.

193
00:15:33,880 --> 00:15:35,930
How's your review of them?

194
00:15:42,110 --> 00:15:47,530
Usually, this Crown Prince acts even more serious and calm than the solemn Dong Hua,

195
00:15:47,530 --> 00:15:52,480
but today, he showed expressions that can only be seen in a young lad.

196
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:54,920
It's really difficult.

197
00:15:57,820 --> 00:16:00,440
I have something to discuss with you.

198
00:16:01,940 --> 00:16:04,300
Qian Qian, why are you suddenly so serious?

199
00:16:04,300 --> 00:16:06,390
I wonder what it is.

200
00:16:08,100 --> 00:16:10,600
It's not something serious.

201
00:16:12,070 --> 00:16:15,280
I will recuperate in Nine Heavens for a few days.

202
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:20,190
Since I came here quietly and didn't use my High Goddess status,

203
00:16:20,190 --> 00:16:23,850
I can't let you openly set up a bedchamber for me.

204
00:16:23,850 --> 00:16:29,030
Why don't I stay at Mochi's Qingyun Hall and make do for a few days?

205
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:32,580
You want to live in Ah Li's Qingyun Hall?

206
00:16:33,330 --> 00:16:36,170
Is it not convenient?

207
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:39,800
I...

208
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:42,680
I have set up a bedchamber for you.

209
00:16:53,810 --> 00:16:58,670
By the way, about my teacher...

210
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:03,730
No one will find out.

211
00:17:24,220 --> 00:17:26,410
You have peach blossoms in your courtyard, too.

212
00:17:26,410 --> 00:17:29,400
Did you move them from the Peach Garden?

213
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:31,730
I planted these 300 years ago.

214
00:17:31,730 --> 00:17:34,910
They finally blossomed after all these years.

215
00:17:36,170 --> 00:17:39,060
They blossomed for the first time after 300 years?

216
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:41,390
You have patience.

217
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:57,240
[Courtyard of Moonlight]

218
00:17:58,630 --> 00:18:01,070
"Courtyard of Moonlight?"

219
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:04,100
It's a good name.

220
00:18:04,100 --> 00:18:07,720
It fits your Pure Wutong Palace.

221
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:15,460
Since I stepped into this courtyard,

222
00:18:15,460 --> 00:18:18,980
I've been feeling off and uncomfortable. Why?

223
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:22,670
High Goddess, please have some tea.

224
00:18:22,670 --> 00:18:24,220
Okay.

225
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:28,340
My Lady?

226
00:18:29,360 --> 00:18:31,750
My Lady, it's indeed you!

227
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:33,620
I've waited for you for 300 years.

228
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:36,100
You're finally back.

229
00:18:36,950 --> 00:18:39,930
Your Highness the Crown Prince, the Soul-Gathering Lamp is truly a sacred relic.

230
00:18:39,930 --> 00:18:43,340
The creation is identical.

231
00:18:45,190 --> 00:18:49,710
Young Immortal, you must have recognized the wrong person.

232
00:18:49,710 --> 00:18:51,790
I'm Bai Qian from Green Hill.

233
00:18:51,790 --> 00:18:54,330
I'm not who you're speaking of.

234
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:03,770
Nai Nai, this is the High Goddess of Green Hill, Bai Qian.

235
00:19:03,770 --> 00:19:06,070
She'll be living here for a while.

236
00:19:06,070 --> 00:19:08,450
Please take care of her.

237
00:19:08,450 --> 00:19:10,430
Get up.

238
00:19:21,350 --> 00:19:24,720
She will be going to Lord of Lingbao's Heavenly Spring afterward.

239
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:27,130
Make the preparations first.

240
00:19:27,130 --> 00:19:29,090
Yes.

241
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:37,550
Go rest up.

242
00:19:37,550 --> 00:19:39,230
I'll bring Ah Li here.

243
00:19:39,230 --> 00:19:41,060
Sure.

244
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,830
What?!

245
00:19:53,770 --> 00:19:56,520
High Goddess Bai Qian is here?

246
00:19:56,520 --> 00:19:58,040
Yes, Your Highness.

247
00:19:58,040 --> 00:19:59,790
She just entered from the southern gates.

248
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:02,300
She's now in Courtyard of Moonlight.

249
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:04,310
What did you say?

