502
00:39:40,610 --> 00:39:44,760
Su Jin, you do treasure friendship.

503
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:47,330
If you really can't bear for Princess Miao Qing to leave,

504
00:39:47,330 --> 00:39:51,600
why not ask Heavenly Monarch to put out a decree and let you marry into the Eastern Sea?

505
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:53,370
What do you think?

506
00:39:53,370 --> 00:39:56,710
Your Mighty Monarch, I temporarily lost my sanity,

507
00:39:56,710 --> 00:39:59,980
so I used this aphrodisiac soup to try to seduce you.

508
00:39:59,980 --> 00:40:04,190
Your Mighty Monarch, I won't object to whatever punishment you give me.

509
00:40:04,190 --> 00:40:07,680
Even if I have to suffer 49 heavenly lightning strikes every day,

510
00:40:07,680 --> 00:40:09,800
I don't care!

511
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:13,340
I beg of you, don't kick me out.

512
00:40:13,340 --> 00:40:20,690
My only wish in my life is to stay with you and serve you forever.

513
00:40:22,220 --> 00:40:24,100
Your Highness! Your Highness!

514
00:40:24,100 --> 00:40:27,720
I have wronged you in the past, and you helped me once.

515
00:40:27,720 --> 00:40:31,210
Please help me again.

516
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:34,100
Your Highness.

517
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:39,620
Since Princes Miao Qing is begging me,

518
00:40:40,390 --> 00:40:44,060
I can't bring myself to beg you back.

519
00:40:44,060 --> 00:40:46,450
I should say something.

520
00:40:46,450 --> 00:40:48,220
Go ahead.

521
00:40:49,260 --> 00:40:53,800
In this situation, Princess Miao Qing's not the only one at fault.

522
00:40:54,500 --> 00:40:59,490
You did know at that time that she liked you yet you brought her here to Heaven.

523
00:40:59,490 --> 00:41:05,310
I know you wanted to repay the debt for Ah Li by helping her avoid her marriage

524
00:41:05,310 --> 00:41:08,240
and send her back once she'd thought it through,

525
00:41:08,240 --> 00:41:10,790
but that's not what she had in mind.

526
00:41:10,790 --> 00:41:14,500
She must've thought you liked her, too.

527
00:41:15,470 --> 00:41:17,250
You gave her this thought,

528
00:41:17,250 --> 00:41:20,380
and you pretended to be a gentleman by not taking action.

529
00:41:20,380 --> 00:41:24,020
She would naturally be forced to make the first move.

530
00:41:24,870 --> 00:41:29,960
But back then, she said she was fine with being a maidservant at Pure Wutong Palace.

531
00:41:31,710 --> 00:41:35,860
Do you believe what a woman says when she's in love with you?

532
00:41:40,290 --> 00:41:43,070
Just listen to me.

533
00:41:43,070 --> 00:41:45,690
You should return to the Eastern Sea immediately.

534
00:41:57,270 --> 00:42:00,800
She is my wife

535
00:42:00,800 --> 00:42:04,210
and the only consort in this Pure Wutong Palace.

536
00:42:05,720 --> 00:42:08,040
Since she has spoken,

537
00:42:08,040 --> 00:42:10,640
Princess Miao Qing, please go back to the Eastern Sea.

538
00:42:14,040 --> 00:42:15,330
Your Mighty Monarch.

539
00:42:15,330 --> 00:42:18,610
Your Mighty Monarch. Your Mighty Monarch!

540
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:54,910
”Cold” by Aska Yang & Diamond Zhang

541
00:42:54,910 --> 00:42:57,100
♫ The temperature gradually drops as night falls ♫

542
00:42:57,100 --> 00:42:59,650
♫ Fallen blossoms become frost ♫

543
00:42:59,650 --> 00:43:04,920
♫ In the distance, you are gazing out afar and exhausting the twilight hours ♫

544
00:43:04,920 --> 00:43:14,200
♫ Without considering the difficulty of forgetting each other ♫

545
00:43:16,310 --> 00:43:18,370
♫ Tender peach blossoms are cold ♫

546
00:43:18,370 --> 00:43:23,590
♫ How could you bear to let go of so many uncertain hearts in the previous lifetime ♫

547
00:43:23,590 --> 00:43:29,650
♫ And still show no pain, no yearning, and no signs that you were forced? ♫

548
00:43:30,950 --> 00:43:35,800
♫ All are just illusions ♫

549
00:43:37,050 --> 00:43:42,610
♫ During the cold night, my yearning for you runs as a river ♫

550
00:43:42,610 --> 00:43:47,810
♫ And transforming into spring soil to nourish me ♫

551
00:43:47,810 --> 00:43:52,290
♫ The fleeting years fill up my lover’s sleeve ♫

552
00:43:52,290 --> 00:43:58,480
♫ Pieces of flowers and plants flow into the waters ♫

553
00:43:58,480 --> 00:44:03,880
♫ The cold will of heaven dresses in glittering colors of flowers ♫

554
00:44:03,880 --> 00:44:09,060
♫ And fall into the mortal realm to hurt my feelings ♫

555
00:44:09,060 --> 00:44:11,900
♫ Calamities are easy to overcome, but trials of love are difficult to overcome ♫

556
00:44:11,900 --> 00:44:21,610
♫ My depreciating heart still holds some hatred from
my previous life ♫

557
00:44:27,890 --> 00:44:33,040
♫ The cold three lives and three worlds are as sudden
as a dream ♫

558
00:44:33,040 --> 00:44:38,610
♫ The wind dries my tears in those instantaneous years ♫

559
00:44:38,610 --> 00:44:42,970
♫ If we can no longer recognize our memories ♫

560
00:44:42,970 --> 00:44:49,120
♫ Then allow our love to rest deep within the dust ♫

561
00:44:49,120 --> 00:44:54,410
♫ When will the cold ten miles of peach blossoms
bloom again? ♫

562
00:44:54,410 --> 00:44:59,830
♫ I see a gust of wind under the tree again ♫

563
00:44:59,830 --> 00:45:02,560
♫ Fallen blossoms are of love, flowing waters are of heartlessness ♫

564
00:45:02,560 --> 00:45:11,840
♫ Don’t allow our past grudges, love, and hate to chill the innocence of the flower ♫

565
00:45:13,320 --> 00:45:23,860
♫ My hope in this lifetime is to be with you ♫
